<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1877] Radial Shading (type 3) fails Ghent Workgroup tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1877</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;GWG 6.0 test: the black rectangle around the circle is missing&lt;br/&gt;
GWG 6.1 test: The rectangles are there but shouldn&apos;t be. Plus, the second type 3 shading has wrong colors. (Maybe same problem as in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1876&quot; title=&quot;Incorrect color for DeviceN type 4 shading object&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-1876&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-1876&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ?)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
